<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Upload de Imagem</title>
    <!-- Adicionando a biblioteca Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: "Ubuntu", sans-serif;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: "Ubuntu", sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            width: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .alert {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Upload Single File</h1>

    <div class="container text-align">
        <div class="alert alert-warning mt-3" role="alert">
            Indique o número do ID da imagem que você gostaria de alterar na URL após o upload/.
            Exemplo: "upload/4", irá alterar imagem de id 4.
        </div>

        <form action="/upload/<%= id %>" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <label for="file">Escolha um arquivo:</label>
            <input type="file" name="image">
            <br/>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Upload</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
